- **Annual Indian Passenger Vehicle Market Size:** 4.4 million units
- **European Automaker Market Share in India:** Less than 4%
- **Current Luxury Import Volumes:** Approximately 40,000-50,000 units annually
- **Indian Market Production Data (December 2025):**
  - Maruti Suzuki India Ltd.: 52.9% of passenger vehicle production
  - Hyundai Motor India Ltd.: 18.1%
  - Mahindra & Mahindra Ltd.: 10.4%
  - Tata Motors: ~8%
  - Others (including Volkswagen, Skoda, Mercedes-Benz, BMW): <4% combined
